Cell["\<\
Note that an eigenvalue of 0 is found for the unity operator. This \
corresponds to the physical constraint that the sum of all populations is \
constant (assuming a closed system).\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.588074684654171*^9, 3.588074705310858*^9}, {
  3.588079122807129*^9, 3.5880791526856613`*^9}, {3.621614945398889*^9, 
