Cell["\<\
For example, suppose that the DD coupling is 20 kHz, and the correlation time \
is 10 ns. The trajectories of the longitudinal magnetization components are \
now as follows:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.588077356811914*^9, 3.588077376706243*^9}, {
  3.588077407770508*^9, 3.588077437390153*^9}, {3.588077476049389*^9, 
