Cell["\<\
Note the positive sign and the factor (2\[Tau]c) in the expression for the \
Lindbladian relaxation superoperator. These factors derive from eqs. 151 and \
153 of the Bengs & Levitt paper (doi.org/10.1016/j.jmr.2019.106645). \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.816845113917491*^9, 
  3.8168452589809647`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"42525079-2c75-46b8-a7de-\
c3a459ec06fd"],

Cell["\<\
The thermal equilibrium density operator under the same conditions is as \
follows:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.588078649856623*^9, 
  3.588078661095727*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"46ee6356-70c7-4938-8f96-\
