Cell["\<\
Homonuclear dipole-dipole relaxation generates T1 relaxation, but not decay \
of singlet order. The example below employs Lindblad thermalization in the \
extreme narrowing limit. \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.816845380389243*^9, 3.81684539867911*^9}, {
  3.816845525478958*^9, 3.816845538414874*^9}, {3.81684557302953*^9, 
